      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still has tons of life left? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants quality without the 'brand new' price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home.",
