      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension geometry. The factory Variable M Differential Lock provides exceptional mechanical grip out of the apex. While the finish reflects its status as a well-loved driver's car, the internal components are in excellent order, including a recently addressed Vanos system for optimal valve timing. A pure, analog performance machine ready for the enthusiast.",
